data.description: Welcome to this 4 Bedroom, 4 Bath home that offers a formal dining room, large great room and a spacious kitchen with counter space and open concept for a great gathering space. Upstairs includes the 4 bedrooms and 2 Full baths. This home has a patio and large back yard , a gym or rec space in the basement with a full bathroom. Whole home generac generator, 2011 furnace, 2016 hot water tank, sump pump 2021, & Radon system installed.
